{"tid":1376447,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文：希望今日台灣，明日香港","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T13:29:36.000Z","uid":258288,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c216c15719051c6a2ec3df4135a2e0e4c629644d","tid":1376447,"uid":258288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"在台灣，蔡英文總統接受日本放送協會訪問，對大陸剛發表的國防白皮書，表達關注。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文說，白皮書顯示大陸持續加強軍力，並懷有野心，對周邊國家與地區造成影響，台灣亦必須加強防禦能力，並希望與這些國家及地區一起面對。蔡英文又批評，大陸想以「一國兩制」統一台灣，認為是企圖單方面改變兩岸現狀，重申絕不接受。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文又對香港政府加強鎮壓示威者表示關注，希望今日的台灣，成為明日的香港，民主、言論自由都受到保障。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470920-20190728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470920-20190728.htm&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wpo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=79b1837b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470920-20190728.htm&h=8639cc62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470920-20190728.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6b57819aa3a6ec1c7a13cdf9b6f96d6c36a9771b","tid":1376447,"uid":187714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01214e37f72bba9ce4ef01efc0c0862b1cdbe965","tid":1376447,"uid":216417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"下台灣希望大過香港wor...."}]}